readme:
[![This project uses GitHub Actions for continuous integration.](https://github.com/ember-cli/ember-welcome-page/workflows/CI/badge.svg)](https://github.com/ember-cli/ember-welcome-page/actions?query=workflow%3ACI) # ember-welcome-page Displays a nice welcome page for newly generated applications with links to resources. ## Installation ```sh ember install ember-welcome-page ```
Use Glint or <template> tag? - Update your template registry to extend this addon's.
